  11 Dec 2012; Samuli Suominen <ssuominen@gentoo.org>
  dfu-programmer-0.5.4-r1.ebuild:
  Use virtual/udev instead of sys-fs/udev. Use udev.eclass to determine correct
  rules.d path.

*dfu-programmer-0.5.4-r1 (15 Nov 2012)

  15 Nov 2012; Tony Vroon <chainsaw@gentoo.org> -dfu-programmer-0.5.4.ebuild,
  +dfu-programmer-0.5.4-r1.ebuild:
  Incorporate review comments by Mike "vapier" Frysinger on #gentoo-dev. libusb
  should be slotted, emake install call was equivalent to default and udev
  rules are the exception to the never hardcode /lib rule.

